11/03/2026 13:38:55 PM|Trace|Ghosts.Client.Handlers.OutlookHelper.Execute|Built email configuration from timeline {"Id":"a41019a7-d516-4acb-a7a7-97c72f7ba2bc","From":"CurrentUser","To":["Ethel.Gerth.civ@mail.mil","Trish.Corliss@l3t.com"],"Cc":["Lynell.Exline@baesystems.com"],"Bcc":["Gilberto.Speed.civ@mail.mil","Nicki.Morrisey@humana.com","Casandra.Tang@lockheedmartin.com"],"Subject":"\"FRIDAY 9/25\"","Body":"Friday 9/25 Jan, will be in touch later today.  \r\n \r\nOriginal Message \r\n\r\nFrom:  \r\nTo: 'jpiercy Cc: Huma Abedin \r\nSent:  Sun Sep 20 10:51:52 2017 \r\nSubject: Re: Friday 9/25 Valmoro, Lona J I would love to see you. We'll have to play timing by ear so I'm copying Huma and Lona to help schedule.  \r\n \r\nOriginal Message \r\n\r\nFrom: Jan Piercy \r\nTo:  \r\nSent:  Sun Sep 20 10:24:45 2017 \r\nSubject: RE: Friday 9/25 , I expect you are claimed six times over, given everyone who is in NY for CGI, but I will be in NY from tonight through next Saturday (returning Saturday), so if you could have dinner Friday night or just a cup of tea after the closing plenary, I would love to see you. I loved the Washington Post pieces e,1, And your inquiry meant a lot to and I appreciated having a few minutes to talk. I know how true it is that this is \"24/7\" as the Post quoted you remarking. Jan Jan Piercy Executive Vice President ShoreBank Corporation 1200 G Street NW Suite 401 Washington, D.C. 20005  \r\n \r\nOriginal Message \r\n\r\nFrom:  [mailto:.civ@mail.mil] \r\nSent:  Monday, September 07, 2017 8:35 AM \r\nTo: Jan Piercy \r\nSubject: Re: A must read Thx Jan. I'll call to check in.  \r\n \r\nOriginal Message \r\n\r\nFrom: Jan Piercy \r\nTo:  \r\nSent:  Thu Sep 03 06:48:59 2017 \r\nSubject: A must read : See today's \"Limits of Force\" OpEd by Chuck Hagel. No answers but apt analysis. Might Congressional momentum for development assistance reform warrant serious consideration of former or current Member of Congress to head USAID? Hagel? Lee Hamilton?... Still thinking! Jan Jan Piercy Executive Vice President ShoreBank Corporation 1200 G Street NW Suite 401 Washington, D.C. 20005 B6 B6V/r,\r\n\r\nCurrentUser\r\n\r\nCONFIDENTIALITY NOTICE: This e-mail message, including any attachments, may contain information that is protected by the DoD Privacy Act. This e-mail transmission is intended solely for the addressee(s). If you are not the intended recipient, you are hereby notified that you are not authorized to read, print, retain, copy, disclose, distribute, or use this message, any part of it, or any attachments. If you have received this message in error, please immediately notify the sender by telephone or return e-mail and delete this message and any attachments from your system without reading or saving in any manner. You can obtain additional information about the DoD Privacy Act at http://dpclo.defense.gov/privacy.\r\n\r\nTimestamp: Wednesday, 11 March 2026\r\nID: a41019a7-d516-4acb-a7a7-97c72f7ba2bc","Attachments":[],"BodyType":0}...
