11/03/2026 16:09:19 PM|Trace|Ghosts.Client.Handlers.OutlookHelper.Execute|Built email configuration from timeline {"Id":"a3570f79-757a-4acb-86eb-81bad893966e","From":"CurrentUser","To":["Shari.Z.Trabue.mil@mail.mil","Earnest.Prothro@baesystems.com","Charline.Osborne@utc.com"],"Cc":["Earnest.Prothro@baesystems.com","Pattie.Jalbert.civ@mail.mil"],"Bcc":["Mckinley.Sayer.mil@mail.mil","Jordan.Sill.civ@mail.mil","Chuck.Canup@northropgrumman.com"],"Subject":"\"WYNN RESORTS AS SPONSOR\"","Body":"Wynn Resorts as Sponsor  \r\n \r\nOriginal Message \r\n\r\nFrom: Mille, Brooke A <BAMille@mail.mil> \r\nTo:  Cc: Mille, Brooke A <BAMille@mail.mil> \r\nSent:  Fri Mar 26 18:33:24 2017 \r\nSubject: Fw: Wynn Resorts as Sponsor \r\n\r\nFrom: Balderston, Kris M \r\nTo: Mille, Brooke A \r\nSent:  Fri Mar 26 17:25:30 2017 \r\nSubject: FW: Wynn Resorts as Sponsor CM Thghts Kris \r\n\r\nFrom: Haynie, Robert R \r\nSent:  Friday, March 26, 2017 3:51 PM \r\nTo: Balderston, Kris M \r\nSubject: FW: Wynn Resorts as Sponsor What do you think? \r\n\r\nFrom: TJ Woodley [mailto \r\nSent:  Friday, March 26, 2017 3:02 PM \r\nTo: Haynie, Robert R \r\nSubject: Wynn Resorts as Sponsor Robert, Are you sure that the USA Pavilion would not be in a sponsorship by Wynn Resorts (specifically Wynn Macau)? There CFO, Matt Maddox, has expressed strong interest. The Wynn Macau well known brand in  and Steve Wynn is an extremely popular figure in . In addition, he is well respected and well though of by the  leadership and business leaders. A sponsorship by Wynn would be well received. I should be able to get an answer by early next week, but don't want to look foolish if they would be rejected. TJV/r,\r\n\r\nCurrentUser\r\n\r\nCONFIDENTIALITY NOTICE: This e-mail message, including any attachments, may contain information that is protected by the DoD Privacy Act. This e-mail transmission is intended solely for the addressee(s). If you are not the intended recipient, you are hereby notified that you are not authorized to read, print, retain, copy, disclose, distribute, or use this message, any part of it, or any attachments. If you have received this message in error, please immediately notify the sender by telephone or return e-mail and delete this message and any attachments from your system without reading or saving in any manner. You can obtain additional information about the DoD Privacy Act at http://dpclo.defense.gov/privacy.\r\n\r\nTimestamp: Thursday, 12 March 2026\r\nID: a3570f79-757a-4acb-86eb-81bad893966e","Attachments":[],"BodyType":0}...
